Variation. Specimens from Miljakovac (Belgrade) differ from the above description as follows: Slightly smaller (
Tab. 3
). Index "length of tegmen: length of pronotum" more variable but with about the same mean (male 0.9–1.3 , mean 1.02 ). Spot on male tegmen blackish brown. Epiproct in male from subquadrate to transverse, apico-lateral angles rounded and slightly concave in between. Subgenital plate in male with triangular apical lobes smaller. Cerci of female subobtuse to obtuse. Subgenital plate of female transversely rounded; in females from Zlatibor it is either rounded or triangular. Ovipositor shorter (
Tab. 2
).
